data.description: NEW Interior Paint just done! Charming well maintained home with 3 bedrooms/ 2 bathrooms and a good sized garage. Freshly painted exterior, new LED lights, newer (2Y) ROOF, new Hurricane doors & windows(9mth), and a survey ($450) was conducted just over a year ago. Electric lawn mower, edger and weed-eater convey to make yard work easy and affordable. Inside, you'll find high-quality, recently replaced appliances(9mth) including the hot water heater, stove, dishwasher, fridge, and microwave. Spanish Tile floors are throughout so NO CARPET and a cozy fireplace to enjoy a cup of cocoa. The Solar panel system was installed 9 months ago, which slashes your bill to around $150 a month TOTAL! No HOA, a screened-in porch, a good sized fully fenced yard for the kiddos and your furbabies!
